  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073820/extras/5b359286e2b0562ae9b29960cf32f6e6.avif?t=1770317596\" width=600 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Curse Rounds is a frantic roguelike in which you must try to survive random rounds, accumulating one curse per room from the 60+ cards available in the game. Kill enemies with a variety of incredible shots and power-ups. No two attempts are ever the same. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073820/extras/d9b6c9ef41211d2afb14135972668b0a.poster.avif?t=1770317596\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073820/extras/d9b6c9ef41211d2afb14135972668b0a.webm?t=1770317596\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073820/extras/5b359286e2b0562ae9b29960cf32f6e6.avif?t=1770317596\" width=600 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Curse Rounds is a frantic roguelike in which you must try to survive random rounds, accumulating one curse per room from the 60+ cards available in the game. Kill enemies with a variety of incredible shots and power-ups. No two attempts are ever the same. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073820/extras/d9b6c9ef41211d2afb14135972668b0a.poster.avif?t=1770317596\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073820/extras/d9b6c9ef41211d2afb14135972668b0a.webm?t=1770317596\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
